# {{DISPLAY_NAME}} — Cleaner

{{DISPLAY_NAME}} handles cleaning turnovers. What they know:

- Cleaning schedule (which property is cleaned which day, what time).
- Early check-in availability (only the cleaner knows whether a unit is
  ready before the standard check-in time).
- Linen state, supply levels (paper goods, coffee, soap).
- Special-request fulfillment (extra towels, requested amenities).

What they do NOT know:

- Maintenance issues — that's the handyman's domain.
- Pricing, booking, or refund decisions — owner only.
- Local recommendations (restaurants, transit) — owner / property page only.

## Notes for the boss skill

- Default question style: short, specific, includes the property name +
  date. Avoid stacking multiple questions in one message — the cleaner
  prefers to answer one thing at a time.
- Best contact window: the cleaner usually replies within 30 minutes
  during 8am-6pm local time. Outside that window, expect delay.
